Organisation Overview (continued)

Services provided by lskandia Energy Operating, Inc.

The Group‘s oil properties have been operated by lskandia Energy Operating, Inc., since 1 August, 2016 for the East Texas basin and since 1 March, 2017 for the Delaware basin. lskandia Energy Operating, Inc is a wholly owned subsidiaw of lskandia Energy Limited, the Group’s parent company. lskandia Energy Operating, Inc. was incorporated to operate the Group's oil properties and to apply the appropriate sophisticated enhanced oil recovery technologies.

As at 31 December 2017 lskandia Energy Operating, Inc. employed 28 (2016: 7) professionals dedicated to the Group’s services including experienced petroleum engineers, an environment, health and safety expert, seasoned field superintendents, production foremen and pumpers.

A|| leases are publicly available on the RailRoad Commission of Texas website (www.rrc.state.tx.us) under lskandia Energy Operating, Inc. (Operator number 426961).
